methods.name: GetAllMeshGeometry
methods.doc: Get the unique IDs of all mesh geometry.

methods.name: GetAllMeshGeometryNotInstanced
methods.doc: Get the unique IDs of all non-instanced mesh geometry.

methods.name: GetAllMeshInstanceUids
methods.doc: Get the unique IDs of all mesh instances.

methods.name: GetAllMeshInstanceUidsUsingMeshGeometryUid
methods.doc: Get all instanced mesh UIDs that use the mesh geometry unique ID.

methods.name: GetAllSkinnedMeshGeometry
methods.doc: Get the unique IDs of all skinned mesh geometry.

methods.name: GetAllSkinnedMeshInstance
methods.doc: Get the unique IDs of all skinned mesh instances.

methods.name: GetAllStaticMeshGeometry
methods.doc: Get the unique IDs of all static mesh geometry.

methods.name: GetAllStaticMeshInstance
methods.doc: Get the unique IDs of all static mesh instances.

methods.name: GetMeshGeometryByUid
methods.doc: Get the geometry mesh from the unique ID.

methods.name: GetMeshGeometrySkeletonRootUid
methods.doc:
Return the skeleton root node UID. This is the UID for a UInterchangeSceneNode that has a "Joint" specialized type.
Return an empty string if the MeshGeometryUid parameter points to nothing.

methods.name: GetMeshInstanceByUid
methods.doc: Get the instanced mesh from the unique ID.

methods.name: GetMeshInstanceSkeletonRootUid
methods.doc:
Return the skeleton root node UID. This is the UID for a UInterchangeSceneNode that has a "Joint" specialized type.
Return an empty string if the MeshInstanceUid parameter points to nothing.

methods.name: IsValidMeshGeometryUid
methods.doc: Return true if there is an existing FInterchangeMeshGeometry that matches the MeshInstanceUid key.

methods.name: IsValidMeshInstanceUid
methods.doc: Return true if there is an existing FInterchangeMeshInstance that matches the MeshInstanceUid key.
